    m_RichText: 1
    m_HorizontalOverflow: 0
    m_VerticalOverflow: 0
    m_LineSpacing: 1
  m_Text: "We have included a Save/Load example called  vSaveLoadInventory.\nUse
    the method SaveInventory to save the Items you currently have on the Inventory.
    \n\n<i><size=10>Ps* This is a Inventory exclusively save/load example, it will
